kin-dza-dza ! ( russian : кин-дза-дза ! , translit . kin-dzah-dza ! ) is a 1986 soviet sci-fi dystopian black comedy cult film released by the mosfilm studio and directed by georgiy daneliya , with a story by georgiy daneliya and revaz gabriadze .   the movie was filmed in color , consists of two parts and runs for 135 minutes in total .   like many of daneliya 's works , kin-dza-dza !   represents a double entendre in terms of parody and features dark and grotesque aspects of humanity .   it depicts a desert planet , depleted of its resources , home to an impoverished dog-eat-dog society with extreme inequality and oppression .